blog-2017-02-18-download-title = You broke our download server \!\! \:D
blog-2017-02-18-download-content = <div><p>Hello guys,<br/>\nso as you can see, our update servers are actually overloaded. You are too many users updating their recalbox, so servers have too many connextions in same time.<br/>\nWe were not prepared to this. We didn't have this kind of problem with previous releases.<br/>\nSo, we scaled the servers and added mirrors. Once cache filled on these mirrors, the sirtuation should come back to normal.<br/>\nThank you to be patient and for your understanding.<br/>\nPS\: For your information, once your recalbox on standby, the current download still progress. But once done, the screen won't refresh to display the reboot message.<br/>\nSo, sometimes, move your gamepad to wake up your recalbox ;)<br/><br/>\n<p>\nYou can follow the progression of the issue on twitter \: <a href\="https\://twitter.com/recalbox">@recalbox</a></p>\n</div>
